Package: groupR
Type: Package
Title: Comprehensive manipulation of dataset with applications in forecasting
Version: 0.2.0
Author: Alex Thompson
Maintainer: Alex Thompson <alexthompson1991@hotmail.com>
Description: In a business setting, there can be a number of demands for a particular "break-out" of data.
    This package is designed to comprehensively work through every single combination of data breakouts with the granular dataset.
    The groupings are defined, functions are applied, and a structured list of results is returned which aggregates the data using the given functions.
    A number of time series functions are available as well to facilitate analysis and even forecasting.
